import React from 'react';
import {Line} from 'react-chartjs-2';
import {Chart as ChartJS,
  LineController,
  LinearScale,
  TimeScale,
  Title,
  Tooltip,
  Legend,
  CategoryScale,
  PointElement,
  LineElement,
  Filler,
  TitlePlugin,
  TooltipPlugin,
  LegendPlugin
} from 'chart.js/auto';

ChartJS.register(
  LineController,
  LinearScale,
  TimeScale,
  Title,
  Tooltip,
  Legend,
  CategoryScale,
  PointElement,
  LineElement,
  Filler,
  TitlePlugin,
  TooltipPlugin,
  LegendPlugin
);

function LineChart({chartData}) {
  return (
    <Line data={chartData}/>
  )
}

export default LineChart
